M., Park, J., Faghaninia, A., Woods-Robinson, R., Persson, K. A., Jain, A. Efficient calculation of carrier scattering rates from first principles. Nat. Commun. 12, 2222 (2021) ``` Interested in contributing? See our [contribution guidelines](https://github.com/hackingmaterials/amset/blob/main/CONTRIBUTING.md)
